programme.title: The Open Live
programme.desc: Coverage of the fourth day of the Major, which takes place at Royal Birkdale Golf Club in Southport, with Henrik Stenson starting as the reigning champion. The Swede entered the final day at last year's tournament with a one-stroke lead over his nearest rival, Phil Mickelson, and produced a stellar eight-under 63 in the fourth round to ensure he claimed victory by three strokes. That round also saw Stenson break the aggregate scoring record for all Major championships, and is now regarded by many pundits as one of the greatest final rounds to ever be played

programme.title: Grand Slam Wimbledon 2017 - Finale (moški): Čilić - Federer
